		"description": "<p>You have inherent magical talent and have trained to fight with weapons, carrying forth the age-old tradition of warrior-mages. You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Your Strength, Dexterity, or Charisma score increases by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li>\n<li>You gain proficiency with the Cutting Omen combat tradition and two maneuvers from it that you could learn. They do not count against your maneuvers known.</li>\n<li>You learn two cantrips of the <em>weaponry </em>school as sorcerer cantrips. They do not count against your cantrips known.</li>\n<li>You gain the following feature:&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Extra Attack</h2>\n<p>At 5th level you can attack twice, instead of once, whenever you take the Attack action on your turn.</p>",
